headline: Is It Too Late To Consider AT&T (T) After Its Recent 20% Share Price Jump
summary: If you are wondering whether AT&T's share price still offers value after its recent run, this breakdown will walk through what the current market price really implies. Over the last month, AT&T's share price has moved to US$28.52, with a 20.9% return over 30 days, 16.1% year to date and 11.3% over the past year. This naturally raises questions about upside potential and changing risk perceptions. Recent news flow around AT&T has focused on its position in the US telecom sector, including...
